---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Features — EnDroit" description="Every tool legal education creators need: script studio, captioned renders, multi-platform publishing, analytics and team workspace.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="badge">Features</div>
      <h1>The workspace built for legal education creators</h1>
      <p class="page-lead">
        Six modules that work together. Replace your stack of Notion + CapCut +
        Buffer + Google Sheets with a single tool that understands legal content.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="block">
        <div class="block-text">
          <span class="kicker">Script studio</span>
          <h2>Write scripts that respect the law and the algorithm.</h2>
          <p>
            The script editor is purpose-built for legal content. Every draft has a
            hook field, a body field, a CTA field — and the auto-disclaimer engine
            inserts the right legal-notice template based on the jurisdiction you
            select.
          </p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Hook + body + CTA structure enforced by the editor</li>
            <li>Source citation field per claim (legifrance.gouv.fr, EUR-Lex, etc.)</li>
            <li>Auto-disclaimer templates for French, Belgian and Swiss law</li>
            <li>AI-assisted rewrites with audit trail (who changed what, when)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="block-visual">
          <div class="mock script-mock">
            <div class="mock-toolbar">
              <span class="mock-tab active">Hook</span>
              <span class="mock-tab">Body</span>
              <span class="mock-tab">CTA</span>
              <span class="mock-tab">Sources</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-body">
              <p class="mock-line"><strong>TON PATRON NE PEUT PAS</strong> te demander de signer une rupture conventionnelle sous pression.</p>
              <p class="mock-line muted">↳ Citation : Cass. soc., 23 mai 2013, n° 12-13.865</p>
              <p class="mock-line muted">⚠️ Disclaimer auto : « Ces informations ne constituent pas un avis juridique. »</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="block reverse">
        <div class="block-text">
          <span class="kicker">Captioned renders</span>
          <h2>Render captioned videos that look like CapCut, in seconds.</h2>
          <p>
            EnDroit produces 1080×1920 vertical MP4s with kinetic captions, scene
            transitions and royalty-free background footage. Renders happen
            on our servers — no waiting on a laggy laptop.
          </p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Word-synced captions with reading-speed safety (max 2.5s / group)</li>
            <li>21 scene types: stat, warning, callout, list, comparison, illustration…</li>
            <li>Royalty-free Pexels stock library, queryable in plain English</li>
            <li>Built-in voice synthesis (ElevenLabs) or import your own recording</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="block-visual">
          <div class="mock render-mock">
            <div class="render-canvas">
              <div class="render-overlay">15 000 €<br/><em>D'AMENDE</em></div>
              <div class="render-progress"><div class="render-bar"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="render-meta">
              <span>Rendering · 67% · 38s remaining</span>
              <span>1080×1920 · 30fps · h.264</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="block">
        <div class="block-text">
          <span class="kicker">Multi-platform publish</span>
          <h2>One video, three platforms, three sets of hashtags.</h2>
          <p>
            Each platform's algorithm responds to different tags. EnDroit splits
            your hashtag pool automatically: TikTok gets trending tags, Instagram
            gets niche tags, YouTube gets descriptive tags. No more copy-paste.
          </p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Connected accounts: TikTok, Instagram Reels, YouTube Shorts</li>
            <li>Per-platform hashtag adaptation (TikTok: 5, IG: 5, YT: 5)</li>
            <li>Platform-specific titles and descriptions, edited side by side</li>
            <li>Publish immediately or schedule for peak hours</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="block-visual">
          <div class="mock publish-mock">
            <div class="platform">
              <span class="platform-icon" style="background:#FF3B30">TT</span>
              <div>
                <strong>TikTok</strong>
                <span class="muted">#fyp #pourtoi #droittiktok #cdd #prudhommes</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform">
              <span class="platform-icon" style="background:#E1306C">IG</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Instagram Reels</strong>
                <span class="muted">#droitdutravail #cdd #precarite #salarie #avocat</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform">
              <span class="platform-icon" style="background:#FF0000">YT</span>
              <div>
                <strong>YouTube Shorts</strong>
                <span class="muted">#droit #cdd #travail #legal #france</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Three more modules</div>
      <h2>Built for repeatable production</h2>

      <div class="cards-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🗓️</div>
          <h3>Scheduling</h3>
          <p>Drag-and-drop calendar across all platforms. Time-zone aware. Set a posting cadence and forget about it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Analytics</h3>
          <p>Unified dashboard for views, watch-time, shares and saves. See which hooks and topics actually convert.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
          <h3>Team workspace</h3>
          <p>Invite editors, reviewers and legal advisors. Roles, approvals, audit trail. Built for firms and creator teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-strip">
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-size:28px">Ready to ship faster?</h2>
          <p>Beta seats are limited. Apply today.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Apply for beta access</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 72px 0 56px;
  }
  .page-hero .badge { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 52px); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .page-lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 620px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .block.reverse .block-text { order: 2; }
  .block-text .kicker {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.8px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .block-text h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 30px; }
  .block-text p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .check-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 28px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .check-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  /* ── Mocks ── */
  .mock {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 48px -16px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
  }
  .mock-toolbar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface-2);
  }
  .mock-tab {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .mock-tab.active { background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent); }
  .mock-body { padding: 20px; }
  .mock-line { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .mock-line.muted { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }

  .render-mock { padding: 16px; }
  .render-canvas {
    aspect-ratio: 9/16;
    max-height: 320px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1410, #0a0508);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .render-overlay {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .render-overlay em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
  .render-progress {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 14px;
    left: 14px;
    right: 14px;
    height: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .render-bar {
    height: 100%;
    width: 67%;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .render-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 4px 4px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .publish-mock { padding: 8px; }
  .platform {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .platform:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .platform-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .platform strong { display: block; color: #fff; font-size: 14px; }
  .platform .muted { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-top: 2px; }

  .cards-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .cards-3 .feature-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .cards-3 h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cards-3 p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55; }

  .cta-strip {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .cta-strip p { color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; font-size: 15px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .block, .block.reverse .block-text { grid-template-columns: 1fr; order: 0; }
    .block { gap: 32px; }
    .cards-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; text-align: left; }
  }
</style>
